Description: Terminal UI for monitoring AI coding agents
 agtop is a top-style terminal UI that surfaces every AI coding agent running
 on the system: Claude Code, Codex, Aider, Cursor, Gemini, Goose, Continue,
 Opencode, Copilot CLI, and more. It shows live PID, command, working
 directory, RSS, CPU%, uptime, files being written, and recent activity, plus
 a panel for Claude Code session state (active / waiting / completed /
 subagents) and Chart-widget history of CPU, memory, and active-agent count.
 .
 Implemented as a static Rust binary (ratatui + crossterm + clap), no runtime
 dependencies beyond a working terminal.

